<br>
Now she was entering in Chadesia, not knowing if she would be welcomed, she was Roman, not an Amazon, but was now feeling home <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=robin>Robin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 9<br> <font color=#993300>(4/15/02 10:49 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm40.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Livia rides to Chadesia</span><hr size=1> ~As she walked back to her hut, she looked over and saw someone riding up. Quirking a brow to herself, she stopped and stood under a nearby tree. The woman didn't look amazon..but then if you had come across Robin a moon earlier, she hadn't looked anything like what she did today. She looked across from her and spotted Varia and walked over~<br>
